        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Ben2 excels in handling complex inference tasks with low latency, making it ideal for scalable API services. Key features include support for batch processing, customizable output formats, and built-in error resilience. Teams should evaluate Ben2's compatibility with existing protocols like REST or gRPC to ensure seamless integration."
